    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Candidate profile:\n{{ JSON.stringify($('Agent Profile Generation').item.json.output) }}\n\nJob posting:\n- Title: {{ $json.title }}\n- Company: {{ $json.companyName }}\n- Location: {{ $json.location }}\n- Description: {{ $json.description }}\n\nScore this job. Return JSON only.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are job-fit scorer mirroring real ATS + recruiter pipeline. Score single LinkedIn job posting against candidate profile. Output strict JSON only, no prose, no markdown, no code fences.\n\n=== STAGE 1: HARD GATES ===\nApply in order. Any fail → recommendation=\"SKIP\", score capped 0-40.\n\n- mustHaveSkillsGate: candidate matches >=60% of mustHaveSkills against JD body. Below 60% → fail.\n- seniorityGate: candidate yearsOfExperience within [JDrequired-2, JDrequired+4]. Under by >=3 → fail. Over by >=5 → fail (overqualified, salary mismatch).\n- locationGate: JD city == candidate locationQuery.city OR JD allows remote OR candidate remotePreference allows JD mode. Mismatch with no remote → fail.\n- exclusionGate: any exclusions term appears in JD title → fail.\n\n=== STAGE 2: WEIGHTED SCORE (0-100) ===\n\n- titleMatch (20): exact primaryRoles match → 20. Adjacent (Backend↔Fullstack, SDE↔SWE) → 15. Loose overlap → 8. Off-domain → 0.\n- mustHaveSkillsMatch (30): (matched/total) * 30. Aliases allowed (Node.js=NodeJS=Node).\n- niceToHaveSkillsMatch (10): (matched/total) * 10.\n- seniorityMatch (20):\n  - within ±1 of required → 20\n  - under by 2 → 13\n  - over by 2 → 8\n  - over by 3-4 → 4\n  - else → 0\n  If JD silent on years, infer from title (Junior/Mid/Senior/Lead/Staff/Principal).\n- locationMatch (10): same city or remote-friendly aligned with candidate pref → 10. Same metro/state → 7. Hybrid same city → 7. Else → 0.\n- recencyMatch (10): mustHave skills used in candidate's last 2 yrs → 10. 3-4 yrs ago → 5. >5 yrs or unknown → 0.\n\n=== STAGE 3: RED FLAG DEDUCTIONS (floor 0) ===\n\n- JD demands skill candidate fully lacks AND it's mustHave → -15 (also added to redFlags)\n- JD signals job-hopper screening (mentions tenure) and candidate avg tenure <12mo → -8\n- JD requires onsite, candidate remote-only → -10\n\n=== RECOMMENDATION ===\n\n- All gates pass AND score >=75 → \"APPLY\"\n- All gates pass AND score 55-74 → \"REVIEW\"\n- Any gate fail OR score <55 → \"SKIP\"\n\n=== CONSTRAINTS ===\n\n- score: integer 0-100, after deductions, floored at 0\n- recommendation: exactly one of \"APPLY\", \"REVIEW\", \"SKIP\"\n- breakdown caps: titleMatch<=20, mustHaveSkillsMatch<=30, niceToHaveSkillsMatch<=10, seniorityMatch<=20, locationMatch<=10, recencyMatch<=10\n- gatesFailed: array of gate names that failed (empty if all pass)\n- reason: max 300 chars, mention top driver + any failed gate\n- All top-level fields required, arrays empty not omitted\n\nOutput schema:\n{\n  \"score\": number,\n  \"breakdown\": {\n    \"titleMatch\": number,\n    \"mustHaveSkillsMatch\": number,\n    \"niceToHaveSkillsMatch\": number,\n    \"seniorityMatch\": number,\n    \"locationMatch\": number,\n    \"recencyMatch\": number\n  },\n  \"gatesFailed\": [string],\n  \"matchedMustHave\": [string],\n  \"missingMustHave\": [string],\n  \"matchedNiceToHave\": [string],\n  \"redFlags\": [string],\n  \"deductions\": number,\n  \"recommendation\": \"APPLY\" | \"REVIEW\" | \"SKIP\",\n  \"reason\": string\n}"
        }
      },
